{\Large \textbf{\textit{Conclusion}}}\\

The development of the web-based mini-game platform has successfully demonstrated the integration of front-end and back-end web technologies to build an engaging, interactive, and user-friendly application.

{\Large \textbf{\textit{Future Scope}}}\\
\begin{itemize}
    \item Persistent scoring and user authentication
    \item Multiplayer game modes
    \item Real-time leaderboards
    \item Additional games and difficulty levels
    \item Enhanced UI/UX with animations
\end{itemize}

